# ── Secrets — never commit these ──────────────────────────────────────────────
**/.env
**/credentials.json
**/gdrive_token.json

# ── Generated outputs ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
**/outputs/
**/raw_jobs.json
resumes/output/

